com.yworks.yfiles.layout

Class CompositeLayoutStage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.AbstractLayoutStage
      • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.CompositeLayoutStage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILayoutAlgorithm, ILayoutStage

    public class CompositeLayoutStage
extends AbstractLayoutStage
    CompositeLayoutStage allows for combining multiple ILayoutStages.

    The ILayoutStages are organized in a pipeline where additional ILayoutStages can be prepended or appended.

    Each ILayoutStage in the pipeline executes its pre-processing code before calling its successor ILayoutStage. Then, after all subsequent ILayoutStages have finished, it will execute its post-processing code.

    Note that the pipeline only works when all ILayoutStages call their core layout algorithm which is the next ILayoutStage in the pipeline.

    • Method Detail

      • appendStage

        public void appendStage(ILayoutStage stage)
        Appends a ILayoutStage to the previously added ILayoutStages.

        The added ILayoutStage will be invoked just before the core layout algorithm will be invoked. Its pre-processing code will be executed after the already added ILayoutStages' pre-processing code, while its post-processing code will be executed before the post-processing code of all the other ILayoutStages.

        Parameters:
        stage - the stage to append

      • prependStage

        public void prependStage(ILayoutStage stage)
        Prepends a ILayoutStage to the previously added ILayoutStages.

        The added ILayoutStage will be invoked before any other ILayoutStage. Its pre-processing code will be executed before the already added ILayoutStages' pre-processing code, while its post-processing code will be executed after the post-processing code of all the other ILayoutStages.

        Parameters:
        stage - the stage to prepend
